item.title: Probabilistic Deep RL for multi-agent systems
item.description: In this project, we will develop a probabilistic deep reinforcement learning framework that allows for predictive control of complex, physical systems. In particular, we aim at methods that can synthesize controllers in fast-paced, multi-agent settings that involve multiple robotic cars.
